data.description: Welcome home to the Dimora, a brand-new paired home design as part of our Villa Series. The layout of this home features two bedrooms, two bathrooms, a study, an open-concept gathering room, and a kitchen. As you come inside off the covered porch, you are greeted by a flex room. Further down the hall is a bedroom with a walk-in closet and a full bathroom. The home then opens into the gathering room with an electric fireplace and kitchen. Loads of cabinets, a corner pantry, and an island give you plenty of storage. Right around the corner is the owner's suite with a trey ceiling, a private bathroom, and a walk-in closet. Enjoy the great outdoors on the rear extended veranda!
